title: X-Men Unlimited (v1 001 - 050 + v2 001 - 014) (1993 - 2006)
description:
X-Men Unlimited (v1 001 - 050 + v2 001 - 014) (1993 - 2006)


X-Men Unlimited Volume 1

Series of specials mainly focusing on individual characters and what drives them. The series ended with issue 50, and was continued in X-Men Unlimited (volume 2) a few months later.

X-Men Unlimited Volume 2 
 
X-Men Unlimited follows the X-Men during their own adventures. Each issue consisted of 2 short stories, with various characters featured in each.
